(POSTGRESQL SETUP) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Use Docker Compose or native PostgreSQL. PostgreSQL must not be exposed to the internet.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 0 Docker Compose configuration is provided in the repository root:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(docker compose up -d postgres) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
